data.message: A few weeks ago a few people said they accepted my friendship request, funny, I don't remember requesting their friendship. Now I just hit a button where it showed me a whole list of people I supposedly sent requests to. Why would this happen when I didn't do it?

replies.message: Hi Celeste. It sounds like you might have been hacked. If you can log into your account, we recommend changing your password. Our Help Center also has information on how to help secure your account: http://on.fb.me/1hq9wrA  -Ryan
